Class DebitCard

java.lang.Object
BankCard
DebitCard
public class DebitCard extends BankCard
Write a description of class DebitCard here. DebitCard is a child(sub-class) of main parent(main-class) BankCard in which its constructor with 4 parameters as well as setter method is called using super keyword A constructor of DebitCard is made with 6 parameters and boolean attribute is assigned to false Getter method(accessor method) of each attribute is made and a mutator(setter) method of withdrawalAmount is made. A withdraw method is made in which amount,date and pin is accepted as argument which deducts money directly from client account
